Notes: Chico State clinches a first round home game in the upcoming CCAA Championship
Tournament with its 20th win of the season. The Wildcats drained a season-high
13 3-pointers; Hannah Womack scored a career-high 24. Chico State plays its
final regular season home game Saturday against Cal State L.A.
Game.Officials: Dee Hernandez,  Wendy Daily,  Kevin Rose
